<!-- About Us Area Start -->
<div class="contact-area fix mb-95">
    <div class="contact-form pt-110">
        <h1 class="contact-title">About MartFive</h1>
        <p class="lead">Mart Five is a grocery products web store which aims at saving users from the hassle of going out and buying every day necessities.  The online store brings to you different categories such as biscuits and chocolates, breakfast & dairy, grocery and Staples, beverages, baby & kids and Pet Care. You can choose from thousands of products. Mart Five is currently delivering in Lahore only.</p>
        <p class="lead">Mart Five aims to evolve the grocery service industry in Pakistan and we aim to target the people who lead a busy lifestyle to shift them from the traditional method of grocery procurement to a more advance online mode. We will ensure a hassle-free shopping experience for our customers, so that they can spend valuable time and energy somewhere else. </p>
        <p class="lead">
            Mart Five aims to be a very customer centric organization. We intend to focus on complete customer journey of our customers, starting with ordering quality products at competitive pricing, on time delivery and hassle-free return policy.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-address pt-110 pb-100">
        <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/")assets/img/team/MartFive_Team.jpg" alt="">
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- About Us Area End -->